{"tid":2265540,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Tim Cook：今年內有更多驚喜　傳 11 月將會有新 Mac 發佈會","createTime":"2020-10-31T13:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T18:11:24.000Z","uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2f8b6872a18e184d6cd96300c207aeeeae3204","tid":2265540,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/applesiliconbenefits-1280x714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fapplesiliconbenefits-1280x714.jpg&h=19c2239b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple 最近發佈了業績報告，除了公佈上一季的表現之外，總裁 Tim Cook 亦預告今年內將會有更多驚喜產品推出，不過就並未有透露更多的詳情。<br />\n<br />\nTim Cook 在業績報告會上透露「今年商店將會有幾個更刺激的產品」，不過就不願意透露更多的詳情。其實在上一次 iPhone 發佈會之前，坊間已經傳聞除了 iPhone 之外還會有幾個產品在今年內推出，不過仍然未見蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n傳聞中的新版本包括有 AirPods Studio 罩耳式耳機和 AirTags 定位標籤，此外最有可能出現的就是之前曾經預告過的 Apple 自家處理器 Mac 產品，由於最新版本的 MacOS Big Sur 尚未推出，估計新 Mac 機發佈之時就是 Big Sur 正式推出的時候。預計在 11 月內會有另一場集中介紹新 Mac 機的發佈會，屆時相信會有更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n來源：MacRumors"},{"pid":"f746b64145e8d151a97a69241097efdb2915bddf","tid":2265540,"uid":213607,"like":47,"dislike":7,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"咪又係跌 屌你老母"},{"pid":"6dc830eccd9d8bb3ebf725087d6f3a7e83725ad2","tid":2265540,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:59:07.000Z","msg":"arm Mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nairtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c5948ac00ca89c3c1e40f3ceedec14beb97dc1","tid":2265540,"uid":76804,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"iphone12 touchid edition<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127e71c037828b41b37a2e780a13c4191337d86b","tid":2265540,"uid":265925,"li